{"tid":1404472,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢嘅前線巴絲真係好型","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:22:08.000Z","uid":246964,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96be8e3be376a093e4055baf7966b51b94b2cd9b","tid":1404472,"uid":246964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:43:52.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚發夢搭車嗰陣見到一堆full gear嘅巴絲離開（安全啲唔講咩車咩站啦）<br />\n可能誇張咗少少 不過見到佢地嗰一下好似見到偶像咁<br />\n有種見到英雄嘅感覺 唔同嘅係佢地無機甲、無好型嘅武器、個個都好後生<br />\n全部身型都偏瘦 但係嗰種氣勢真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我平時都有發開夢 但係自認無呢種勇氣上前線<br />\n所以想同前線巴絲講聲 你地真係好型好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲激動所以表達奇奇怪怪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw致所有發夢嘅巴絲 無論你前線定後排 每一個都咁叻咁偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34b0d6821ade95c1a0464e6d2c763dd62a5d698","tid":1404472,"uid":246964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9poA54s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9poA54s.png&h=058f0031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8月5日罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a5f02ba29b6f714e1f78e5fca213979737e292","tid":1404472,"uid":246964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/04/124613_5ad5f495af930f7062b825cadfcc4bd1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F04%2F124613_5ad5f495af930f7062b825cadfcc4bd1.png&h=3d0a905a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=